metadata.description:
The Adored Ones are one of the most formidable fighting forces in the world, willing to sacrifice everything to protect its people.

​

An art project filled with Easter Eggs and showing respect to the Dahomey Amazons. The all-female military regiment of the Kingdom of Dahomey, which was located in West Africa - in what is now the Republic of Benin.

The Dahomey Amazons were an inspiration to Marvel when creating the Dora Milaje - the sworn protectors of The Black Panther.

​

Made with love for the people, by the people. 
CC0////\\\\No Discord////\\\\For The Art////\\\\\
